Name: DocumentReferenceStatus
Title: DocumentReferenceStatus
Description: The status of the document reference.

Name: DocumentRelationshipType
Title: Document Relationship Type
Description: The type of relationship between documents.

Name: HTTPVerb
Title: H T T P Verb
Description: HTTP verbs (in the HTTP command line). See [HTTP rfc](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc7231) for details.

Name: FHIRRestfulInteractions
Title: FHIR Restful Interactions
Description: The set of interactions defined by the RESTful part of the FHIR specification.

Name: AuditEventEntityRole
Title: AuditEventEntityRole
Description: Code representing the role the entity played in the audit event.

Name: ParticipationType
Title: ParticipationType
Description: A code specifying the meaning and purpose of every Participation instance. Each of its values implies specific constraints on the Roles undertaking the participation.

Name: BasicAuditEntityType
Title: Entity Types that are defined in IHE BasicAudit
Description: These are new codes used in BasicAudit IG, where AuditEvent.entity is used to hold a specific kind of data that is not covered by the existing valueSet.

Name: MHDlistTypes
Title: MHD List Types
Description: To use the List resource for two different use-cases we define a code-system with the types of List needed in MHD
